items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

items.checkin_comment: Strong alcohol flavour, with a hint of caramel and barely. Nice but not my taste.

items.badge_description: It's time to give bottle shops some love by adding them as your purchased location. That's 290 check-ins with a purchased location! Tag 5 more to get to Level 59.

While spontaneity can be fun, sometimes you want to make sure your adventure will rock. Checkout the menu at an Untappd Verified Venue before visiting and know exactly what’s on tap! That's 485 check-ins at venue that is verified.  Try 5 more for Level 98!
It takes the perfect amount of light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now it’s time to drink it! That’s 125 check-ins with a photo.

items.checkin_comment: #BeerCartelXmas 2020 #AdventBeer 19 - Sweet toffee caramel nose. Big, sweet, smooth and balanced - that's some life! Booze & bitterness balanced by toffee and caramel sweetness. Long, warming, boozy finish!

items.checkin_comment: Advent calendar day 19 catchup. Malty with a touch of marmalade, dried fruit and citrus zest.

items.badge_description: Strong, bold flavors really suit you. The barleywine brings with it a long history dating all the way back to ancient Greece. That's 5 different Barleywine, Wheat Wine Beers or Rye Wine! Try 5 more for Level 2!

Canning is all the rage and it's not hard to see why - travels well, more environmentally friendly, and no need to carry your bottle opener. That's 90 checkins with the serving style of Can. Try 5 more for Level 19!

items.checkin_comment: #advent19 big boi. I think I'm into barleywine now? Even if it sounds like a hobbit drink. Malty, feels the most "Christmassy" in the calendar so far, reminds me of sherry or brandy?? Needs a mince pie.
